quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  3,144,"Ne Mohammad shiyali halali Omurumwa butswa. Toto Abarumwa babura imbeli wuwe, koo nafwa nohomba niyerwa, mulabotokhana mukalukhe inyuma? Ni ubotokhana yakalukha inyuma oyo shakholakhwo shiosishiosi Nyasaye tawe, Ne Nyasaye alarunga bamukhupilanga orio"
  3,145,"Ne omundu shiyakhafwasa tawe halali khubuchami bwa Nyasaye, shingala yahandichilwa, ne owenya omurungo kwokhushialo khwitsa okhumuwa, ne owenya omurungo kwo mwikulu khwitsa okhumuwa, ne alarunga balia bakhupanga orio"
  3,146,"Ne ni Abarumwa benga balwaana ne halala ninabo Abasuubili abaanji bakholanga shichila Nyasaye shibakhola oburi khukabanyoola khunjila ya Nyasaye tawe, nohomba 3. shibateshelekhana nohomba shibatofula, ne Nyasaye yachama abefwilanga"
  3,147,"Ne amakhuwa kabu kalisa okhuboola mbu; ‘’Nyasaye wefu omulesi, khuleshele ebionono biefu, nende okhubura eshichelo khwefu, mumakhuwa kefu, ne tinyisia ebilenje biefu ne okhuhabine khushile omukanda kwabakhayi"
  3,148,"Mana Nyasaye nabahelesia omurungo omulayi kwokhushialo nende omurungo omulayi komwikulu, Ne Nyasaye yachama abakholanga amalayi"